USAGE: meliponto config <OPTIONS>

DESCRIPTION: Sets up the provided flag information to the config file.

OPTIONS:
	--re		string	Sets your employee registration within your company on the config file
	--company	string	Sets your company id number registered within Ahgora into the config file
	--generate		Generates a brand new config file from scratch <Will override current config file>
	--help			Displays the help message for the command
